1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:19,820
Legend of Awakening

3
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:22,579
Episode 17

4
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,880
That guy came here just a few days ago.

5
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,210
He fights only once a day

6
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,240
but he has the highest odds.

7
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,440
What’s his name?

8
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,680
Lu Ping.

9
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:58,600
I just want to beat you!

10
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:08,480
Someone told me that you can use six forces.

11
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:12,960
Have you ever seen one like that

12
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,960
still coming to the ring?

13
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,720
No!

14
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:22,060
You’re right!

15
00:03:22,060 --> 00:03:23,760
I have seen through you.

16
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,440
You can only use two forces,

17
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:30,480
Force of Air and Force of Temperature.

18
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,760
Then unfortunately,

19
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:35,400
I am good at Force of Heft.

20
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,560
You’re dead.

21
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,960
OK.

22
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,600
Beat him!

23
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:45,960
Beat!

24
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,770
You looked down upon me.

25
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,240
I can use more than two forces.

26
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:42,760
Good.

27
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:44,360
Force of Spirit Lock!

28
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:45,880
It’s Lu Ping.

29
00:04:58,880 --> 00:04:59,720
With such a height!

30
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:01,000
He is a fool.

31
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,920
Pay back my money!

32
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,360
Good!

33
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,440
Well done!

34
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,760
Good!

35
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,400
Well done!

36
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,400
Good!

37
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:16,740
[Wuji Manor]

38
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,220
Master,

39
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,600
the bandits who always intrude the border

40
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:23,160
have been killed by our men.

41
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:26,040
People who have been captured are freed.

42
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,720
Well done.

43
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,080
Get some money

44
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,100
to give to them for settling down.

45
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:35,320
Yes.

46
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,140
Master,

47
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:38,720
are you going to

48
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,880
inform the army in Jin City?

49
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:44,159
You must be praised for what you did.

50
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,520
Jin is near the border

51
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:48,840
and very important for the country.

52
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:50,680
The army is busy every day.

53
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:53,210
Why bothering praising ourselves

54
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,920
for killing the bandits?

55
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,920
We learn martial arts

56
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,480
to keep our border

57
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,300
and to protect our people.

58
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,240
This is what we should do.

59
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,280
When I was in Kaifeng,

60
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,840
I heard the chaos made by Shanhai Gang.

61
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,400
You inform the masters of all the sects

62
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,240
for the possible danger

63
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,200
in case of Shanhai Gang’s sneak attack.

64
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:14,800
Yes.

65
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,680
You are awake.

66
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,300
I’m sorry, father.

67
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,960
I come to apologize.

68
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,800
Since you have woken up,

69
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,400
just go out with me.

70
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:28,360
Yes.

71
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:42,500
[Wuji Manor]

72
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:39,520
I heard that you behaved well at the convention

73
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,640
and killed one master of Shanhai Gang.

74
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,240
After these years,

75
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:47,840
you have grown up and been mature.

76
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,210
For all these years,

77
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,180
I left you living by yourself.

78
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,440
I am sorry.

79
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,409
That’s my responsibility.

80
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,760
And it will be yours one day.

81
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:01,120
I didn’t go to find you

82
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:04,440
because I hope you can
solve your own problem.

83
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,120
Only in this way

84
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,320
you can qualify yourself to
be the son of Yan Qiuci,

85
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,920
Wild Sword in the Northwest.

86
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:14,140
I happened to enter Zhaifeng and at that time

87
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,480
I gave up on myself.

88
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,420
Surprisingly, I got a good master

89
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,490
and made some good friends.

90
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:23,520
I did something that I had never thought of.

91
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:24,970
I have gone through many

92
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:27,560
difficulties which I couldn’t solve before.

93
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,520
Now I have found the reason

94
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:30,050
for me to use my sword again.

95
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,440
Father,

96
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,760
I have come back.

97
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,720
In the past, I was worried

98
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,240
that you were too upright

99
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:45,280
to live in the society.

100
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:49,360
But I have some missing observation,

101
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,560
that you have grown up.

102
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,680
I promised to help Lu Ping.

103
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,760
I couldn’t fulfill my words.

104
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,320
But I would certainly help him

105
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:59,480
to punish Shanhai Gang for

106
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:02,240
giving him the Force of Spirit Lock.

107
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:03,440
Good.

108
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,640
We are not only father and son

109
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:10,160
but also allies in the future.

110
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,100
We should think carefully

111
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,980
about fighting against the gang.

112
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,800
You have not recovered completely.

113
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,760
You need to rest.

114
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,720
Go ahead.

115
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,520
Yes.

116
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,280
Master,

117
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:47,000
I have learned that

118
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,840
Guo Youdao was

119
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:52,290
exactly the master of our younger master.

120
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,930
As I thought, my fourth junior.

121
00:08:55,560 --> 00:09:00,000
It’s our fate.

122
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:01,880
Master,

123
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,400
Lu Ping who is the friend of our younger master

124
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:06,720
has the Force of Spirit Lock.

125
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,920
Many people can prove that.

126
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,800
It is not something normal.

127
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:14,540
Except for the younger master that year…

128
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:18,960
He was dead.

129
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,120
It’s too late to say that.

130
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,980
Don’t mention that again.

131
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:25,000
You’ll make Xifan sad.

132
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:25,840
Yes.

133
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:32,720
If I knew that Zhaifeng Institute
was built by him,

134
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,720
I would have come early

135
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,760
instead of watching it destroyed.

136
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,320
Forget it.

137
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,880
It can serve as another reason

138
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:46,880
for us to fight against Shanhai Gang.

139
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:50,820
[Wuji]

140
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,450
Younger master.

141
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,640
Our men have gathered.

142
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,200
Some of us also protect in the outskirt.

143
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,960
You haven’t recovered totally.

144
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,560
Just have a rest.

145
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,720
Lately, I heard Shanhai Gang

146
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,480
came to Jin City.

147
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,740
I want to investigate more

148
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:12,160
too see what they are doing.

149
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:13,440
News!

150
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,120
Younger master!

151
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,040
About five miles away,

152
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,970
we found people from Shanhai Gang.

153
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,860
Fortunately, we met them.

154
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:24,320
Qin Qi is putting a great pressure on the gang.

155
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,440
They are hiding.

156
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,300
It’s not easy to find them.

157
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,770
I can’t lose the chance.

158
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,840
Tell our men to hide themselves.

159
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,480
A Ze, you come with me.

160
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,080
Yes.

161
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:35,800
Go.

162
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:40,800
Master,

163
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:44,090
the guy in the boxing casino has
the Force of Spirit Lock.

164
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,480
The Force of Spirit Lock?

165
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:48,880
Yes.

166
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,600
I have seen clearly with my eyes.

167
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,000
He didn’t even hide his name.

168
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,600
He called himself as Lu Ping.

169
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:58,040
Lu Ping.

170
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,580
I have been looking for you for so long

171
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,620
and I have finally made it.

172
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:03,920
Let’s go to Jin City.

173
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,720
Yes.

174
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,500
Have you heard what they said?

175
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,560
Lu Ping seems to be alive.

176
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:17,760
Tell our men to follow

177
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,600
me to Jin.

178
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:19,360
Yes.

179
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:27,740
[Jin City]

180
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:36,720
Younger master.

181
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,920
I have asked about it.

182
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:39,760
It’s an illegal boxing casino.

183
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,200
Lu Ping was here

184
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,880
playing illegal boxing.

185
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:45,000
Why did he expose himself?

186
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,560
I’ll go to see the situation first.

187
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:50,040
A Ze,

188
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:52,600
you inform the army with our men.

189
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,720
If I don’t come out in 30 minutes,

190
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:55,960
you’ll break the door.

191
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,520
Yes.

192
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,400
For my life,

193
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:43,160
I hate the ones following me the most.

194
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,140
You’ve noticed me in the first place.

195
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:51,500
See! Champion of the convention from Zhaifeng!

196
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,340
Are, are you taking revenge on me?

197
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,680
Or are you going to die here?

198
00:13:30,800 --> 00:13:33,320
Lu Ping, you are alive!

199
00:13:34,920 --> 00:13:36,640
Senior, you always come

200
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,360
at the wrong time.

201
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,560
You did it deliberately!

202
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,980
Only when I am captured by the gang

203
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,760
then  I can take revenge.

204
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:50,300
Do you really think that with only two forces

205
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:52,220
can defeat me who use four forces?

206
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:59,000
You both have nice teeth.

207
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,600
Then stay here together!

208
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,930
The government!

209
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,700
What are you doing inside?

210
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,800
Only when I am captured by the gang

211
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:19,120
I can take revenge.

212
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,720
Master, go.

213
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,210
Take Lu Ping with us.

214
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:07,480
Go.

215
00:15:07,880 --> 00:15:08,840
Retreat.

216
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:19,080
Lu Ping,

217
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:20,680
are you OK?

218
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:23,440
Lu Ping.

219
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,040
Lu Ping.

220
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:29,640
Hurry.

221
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:30,800
Hurry to find younger master.

222
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:31,280
Hurry.

223
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:38,450
Why do you as a disciple of Zhaifeng

224
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:41,320
want to help us?

225
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:50,520
By the way, you are a friend of Lu Ping.

226
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:54,440
We are just ordinary friends.

227
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:55,640
It’s nothing.

228
00:15:57,280 --> 00:15:59,210
I know that Lu Ping exposed himself

229
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,360
just to attract you.

230
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:03,560
So, I want to be one of you.

231
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,440
You want to be one of us?

232
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:09,730
You killed Wen Gecheng, the Master of Wind Division.

233
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:13,640
Why do we believe in you?

234
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,240
I have been learning martial arts since young.

235
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:19,760
I just want to win fame.

236
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:22,360
Zhaifeng is so poor.

237
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,920
What’s more, I won a place

238
00:16:25,040 --> 00:16:26,100
at the convention.

239
00:16:26,160 --> 00:16:28,320
But Qin Qi didn’t care about the truth.

240
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:30,080
It was me who killed the enemy

241
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:32,600
but he asked my life to pay for that.

242
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:34,120
Lu Ping can tolerate such a thing

243
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,120
but I can’t.

244
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:37,940
I would rather choose a new leader

245
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:39,900
than tolerate the insult.

246
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:43,400
That’s why you choose Shanhai Gang.

247
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:46,000
The gang dares to send spies

248
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:47,200
to the country.

249
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:51,040
It must have a big plan.

250
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:54,320
You are brave!

251
00:16:55,760 --> 00:17:00,040
I really need a skilled man in Fire Division.

252
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:03,520
But I have a requirement.

253
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:06,800
I’ll do what you say.

254
00:17:07,829 --> 00:17:09,160
That’s easy.

255
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,829
If you want to be one of us,

256
00:17:12,589 --> 00:17:17,920
you must give yourblood and swear.

257
00:17:19,829 --> 00:17:21,630
All the people who dare to do this

258
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:24,800
is like the brothers of mine.

259
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,200
What do you think?

260
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:30,400
Dare you?

261
00:18:09,800 --> 00:18:10,400
Xifan!

262
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,680
Mr. Lu, you are finally awake.

263
00:18:15,840 --> 00:18:16,840
It’s great!

264
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,000
Miss Ling,

265
00:18:21,520 --> 00:18:23,050
how is it that you are alive?

266
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,400
Elder Guo saved me.

267
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:29,640
Master.

268
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:32,280
He did not just saving my life

269
00:18:32,560 --> 00:18:34,120
but also asked Master Chu Min

270
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:35,560
to take care about me.

271
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:41,560
That’s it.

272
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:53,960
What about Xifan?

273
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:55,160
He…

274
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:57,840
he went with Shanhai Gang.

275
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:00,960
You are lucky.

276
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:03,480
Yan Xifan hurt you badly.

277
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:05,360
His sword was near your heart.

278
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:07,240
You almost died.

279
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:09,280
Near my heart?

280
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:12,600
Xifan is good at sword.

281
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:14,920
How did he do such a thing?

282
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:16,920
Why? You don’t want to live?

283
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:20,600
No.

284
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:23,880
Xifan didn’t want to kill me.

285
00:19:24,760 --> 00:19:27,090
He stabbed me in front of people of thegang

286
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,610
because he wanted to be a spy for me.

287
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,800
It’s so cold!

288
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:52,080
Here! One hot noodle with two eggs!

289
00:19:52,360 --> 00:19:53,000
OK!

290
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:55,120
Have you got information of my brother?

291
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:56,000
Er…

292
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:58,480
I went around the city for three times.

293
00:19:58,480 --> 00:19:59,800
But I haven’t got.

294
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,200
Then how can you still eat?

295
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,360
You go to search!

296
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:04,280
When we arrived at Tianzhao,

297
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:06,000
Master Chu Min wasn’t there.

298
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:07,720
You said the brother’s sense

299
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:08,920
was head to Jin City.

300
00:20:09,360 --> 00:20:10,840
Now we don’t have senior.

301
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:11,600
Master…

302
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,280
We don’t have him either.

303
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:15,000
Brother must be all alone.

304
00:20:15,280 --> 00:20:17,360
What if Shanhai Gang found him?

305
00:20:17,760 --> 00:20:18,490
My disciple,

306
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,360
you have to be sensible.

307
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:21,980
It is raining heavily.

308
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:24,200
Even a dog can’t smell anything.

309
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:25,160
By the way,

310
00:20:25,320 --> 00:20:27,050
can’t you respect your master?

311
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,720
I look like a strong man.

312
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:29,440
In fact,

313
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:30,760
I am weak.

314
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,520
We haven’t had a rest

315
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,360
for so long in Jin.

316
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:37,610
If you don’t go, then I will.

317
00:20:38,600 --> 00:20:38,920
Mister!

318
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,580
-My disciple! -Your noodles.

319
00:20:44,120 --> 00:20:45,720
I haven’t had even one bite!

320
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:46,960
And two eggs!

321
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:51,320
My disciple!

322
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:07,700
Are you sure it’s here?

323
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:09,680
Of course.

324
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:12,320
But we have come here.

325
00:21:14,360 --> 00:21:15,080
You are clever.

326
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:16,800
I just examined you.

327
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:18,520
I never thought you can pass.

328
00:21:21,120 --> 00:21:22,840
It’s there. Let’s go.

329
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:39,440
We had come here.

330
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:45,600
Maybe we are lost.

331
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,160
But don’t worry.

332
00:21:47,520 --> 00:21:48,720
We will get there.

333
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:50,440
Mo Lin,

334
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,410
did you do it deliberately?

335
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:54,380
You just want to have me as your disciple.

336
00:21:54,380 --> 00:21:55,620
No!

337
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,760
Listen to me.

338
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:57,400
I…

339
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:58,760
I…

340
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:01,480
I seem to faint.

341
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:02,480
Who believe?

342
00:22:07,520 --> 00:22:08,040
Mo Lin.

343
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:08,960
Mo Lin.

344
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:24,560
Elder,

345
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:26,360
Mr. Lu didn’t recover

346
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:27,640
and he has got a fever.

347
00:22:27,640 --> 00:22:28,920
He may die.

348
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:30,360
If I don’t allow that,

349
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:32,120
no one can make him die.

350
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:38,140
[Big Dipper Institute]

351
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:38,960
Big Dipper is where the skilled men are.

352
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:41,080
General Qin was kicked out

353
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:42,960
even with the order of the emperor.

354
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:44,360
Lu Ping is from Zhaifeng.

355
00:22:44,520 --> 00:22:45,800
And he is guilty.

356
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:48,360
Can he be accepted?

357
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:52,160
It is none of their business.

358
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:55,610
Who is there breaking into Big Dipper?

359
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:02,680
Master,

360
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:04,400
since the death of Master Leng,

361
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:05,730
we have been declining.

362
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:07,080
Now people in Jianghu all regard Yan Qiuci

363
00:23:07,080 --> 00:23:09,560
from Wuji Manor as the leader.

364
00:23:09,680 --> 00:23:11,640
What a shame!

365
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:14,320
We have seven peaks and five institutes.

366
00:23:14,320 --> 00:23:16,320
Seven peaks represent seven stars in Big Dipper.

367
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:18,920
Master of Yaoguang Peak was missing for years.

368
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,180
No one has heard of him.

369
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:22,960
We must attract new disciples now.

370
00:23:23,080 --> 00:23:25,840
We always explain the vacancy of Master of

371
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:27,840
Yaoguang as due to illness.

372
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:30,380
If it is still so this year,

373
00:23:30,760 --> 00:23:34,120
we pled you to choose a new master.

374
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:40,360
Master of Yaoguang still in her position.

375
00:23:41,080 --> 00:23:44,440
She was out just to treat her hurt.

376
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:45,960
We all know that

377
00:23:46,160 --> 00:23:47,640
she is missing for years.

378
00:23:47,800 --> 00:23:49,860
What’s the use of keeping an old name?

379
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:57,600
Master,

380
00:23:57,720 --> 00:24:00,160
didn’t you behave well before Qin Qi?

381
00:24:02,080 --> 00:24:03,640
He is an outsider.

382
00:24:03,760 --> 00:24:05,640
I have to protect my image.

383
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:14,960
Master,

384
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,880
a crazy woman hurt our men

385
00:24:17,040 --> 00:24:17,920
and broke into the gate.

386
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,200
She headed for the Medicated Diet Room.

387
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:21,000
Who dares to break into Big Dipper?

388
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:22,730
She said she was a friend of you.

389
00:24:22,840 --> 00:24:24,500
You will know once you see her.

390
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:33,780
[Medicated Diet Room]

391
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:33,920
Elder, what should we do?

392
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:36,960
Go in and find the best-looking one.

393
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:39,080
Let him have it.

394
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:42,280
But you have offended all the disciples

395
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,720
by breaking into the gate.

396
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:47,200
Who will save Mr. Lu?

397
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:53,680
The saver is coming.

398
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:04,160
Master, she must be punished.

399
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:06,240
Or we must be shameful.

400
00:25:08,520 --> 00:25:09,520
Li Yaotian.

401
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:10,400
How dare you?

402
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:11,930
You call Master by his name!

403
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,520
Behave yourself.

404
00:25:19,840 --> 00:25:20,840
Senior Chu Min.

405
00:25:22,840 --> 00:25:24,240
I hurried here before

406
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,920
so I didn’t ask people to inform you.

407
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:27,000
I brought a man

408
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:28,020
called Lu Ping.

409
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:30,080
You just decide how many people

410
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:31,240
and how much medicine to cure him.

411
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:33,400
Anyway, he can’t die.

412
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:35,720
Yes.

413
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,600
Don’t worry.

414
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:39,920
Master, this is…

415
00:25:41,600 --> 00:25:43,000
She is the missing Master

416
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:44,320
of Yaoguang,

417
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:46,880
Chu Min.

418
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:50,480
That talented Master Chu Min

419
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:52,320
who can use four forces

420
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:53,520
at the age of 16?

421
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:55,040
Yes.

422
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:57,800
Why are you standing here?

423
00:25:57,800 --> 00:25:59,280
Go right now.

424
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:01,520
Yes.

425
00:26:02,300 --> 00:26:04,860
[Medicated Diet Room]

426
00:26:04,360 --> 00:26:05,040
Stop there.

427
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:43,780
[Qin Family]

428
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:16,280
Sang, you can use Force of Heft now.

429
00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:19,160
Congratulations, Miss!

430
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:21,160
It’s not that hilarious.

431
00:27:21,920 --> 00:27:23,800
You didn’t fight with all your strength.

432
00:27:23,800 --> 00:27:25,080
You look down upon me.

433
00:27:25,840 --> 00:27:28,300
What is the difference between 3 or 4 forces?

434
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:36,040
Sang,

435
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:37,680
I know that

436
00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:39,480
you blame me

437
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,120
for the death of Lu Ping.

438
00:27:43,240 --> 00:27:44,170
What about this?

439
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:45,650
When holiday comes,

440
00:27:45,840 --> 00:27:47,120
I will take you to eat your favorite

441
00:27:47,120 --> 00:27:48,880
hibiscus cakes.

442
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:50,240
Brother,

443
00:27:51,520 --> 00:27:52,800
I’m no longer a child.

444
00:27:59,560 --> 00:28:01,720
Miss has been practicing

445
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:03,240
since the destruction of Zhaifeng.

446
00:28:03,240 --> 00:28:04,500
She has improved a lot.

447
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:53,320
It’s me.

448
00:28:56,560 --> 00:28:57,420
This is for you.

449
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:06,560
I tore your skirt last time.

450
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:11,800
When I see it,

451
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,520
I think you must look…

452
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:15,800
look pretty on it.

453
00:29:31,360 --> 00:29:32,960
Do you know how long I waited?

454
00:29:33,040 --> 00:29:33,600
OK,

455
00:29:35,320 --> 00:29:37,980
I’ll take you to the best restaurant in Kaifeng.

456
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:48,240
Look, shooting stars!

457
00:29:53,840 --> 00:29:54,970
One must be faithful

458
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:56,860
when giving out gifts.

459
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,600
I share my most precious

460
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:02,210
starry sky with you.

461
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:11,620
Didn’t you observe the stars?

462
00:30:13,760 --> 00:30:14,960
Why looking at me?

463
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,200
I…

464
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:23,560
Thank you!

465
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:28,040
You brat.

466
00:30:29,560 --> 00:30:31,240
If I was stronger that day,

467
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:34,320
could I protect Ziyan

468
00:30:39,280 --> 00:30:40,880
and you that day?

469
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:57,960
Master is the leader of Shanhai Gang.

470
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:03,120
There’re four masters for four divisions:

471
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:05,280
Wind, Forest, Mountain and Fire.

472
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:07,160
Wind Division takes charge of information.

473
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:09,840
Spies are under the control of them.

474
00:31:10,040 --> 00:31:12,560
Master takes control of Forest Division.

475
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:15,450
They manage the internal affairs.

476
00:31:16,320 --> 00:31:18,380
Those mad men from Mountain Division

477
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:20,440
always make experiment in the water cell

478
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:21,720
and doing Method of Xi Sui.

479
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:24,240
I am the leader of Fire Division.

480
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:26,440
We kill people.

481
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:28,480
From today,

482
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:31,480
you are one of us.

483
00:31:33,320 --> 00:31:35,400
Yes, master.

484
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:38,240
Once you enter the gang,

485
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:40,800
you can never go out.

486
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:44,760
Don’t you want to exit?

487
00:31:45,360 --> 00:31:46,960
I will give my life to fulfill my duty

488
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:49,360
since I become your man.

489
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,560
You are wise.

490
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:56,800
Master called me today.

491
00:31:57,280 --> 00:31:58,560
Just follow me.

492
00:32:00,040 --> 00:32:00,440
Yes.

493
00:32:06,080 --> 00:32:07,200
Master.

494
00:32:27,360 --> 00:32:28,200
Where is he?

495
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:29,960
Master,

496
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:32,400
I have caught Lu Ping

497
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:34,760
but the woman called Chu Min

498
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,120
hindered me.

499
00:32:36,320 --> 00:32:38,360
She brought people from the government.

500
00:32:38,360 --> 00:32:39,360
I didn’t want to make trouble

501
00:32:39,360 --> 00:32:40,720
so I came back.

502
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:43,600
Chu Min?

503
00:32:43,760 --> 00:32:45,160
I have investigated that

504
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,760
the woman took Lu Ping

505
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:49,160
to Big Dipper.

506
00:32:49,400 --> 00:32:51,260
What if I take people to Big Dipper

507
00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:52,280
to kill them all?

508
00:32:54,320 --> 00:32:56,120
You are overreaching yourself.

509
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:58,940
Skilled people all gather in Big Dipper.

510
00:32:59,320 --> 00:33:00,880
How can you kill them?

511
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:03,340
We have lost the opportunity.

512
00:33:03,640 --> 00:33:04,720
What do you want?

513
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:06,040
I am not giving in!

514
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:11,720
Now our plan in E’zhou is the most important.

515
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:14,280
We can capture Lu Ping later.

516
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:16,600
Go and prepare.

517
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:19,800
You’ll head for E’zhou to arrange later.

518
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:23,200
Don’t make any mistake!

519
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:24,600
OK.

520
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:28,840
E’zhou is on the border between Shuo and Tan.

521
00:33:28,840 --> 00:33:30,000
What are they doing?

522
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:34,560
Master, it’s 5 p.m.

523
00:33:55,320 --> 00:33:56,680
What is master doing?

524
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,800
Master exercises at this time

525
00:33:58,800 --> 00:34:00,080
every day in his secret room.

526
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:01,280
He never takes a rest.

527
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:03,490
Why do you care about it?

528
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:05,840
He has already got such a high position,

529
00:34:05,840 --> 00:34:07,900
yet he shows great self-discipline.

530
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,800
What a great man!

531
00:34:10,230 --> 00:34:11,190
How I admire him!

532
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:40,520
Lu Ping,

533
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:43,460
only when you get into the gang

534
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:44,860
you can face the master

535
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,290
and kill him by one move.

536
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,280
But people here are good at hypnotization

537
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:49,670
using the Force of Spirit.

538
00:34:49,670 --> 00:34:51,929
Fengling Gang was destroyed in this way.

539
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:58,320
Someone has to be the spy.

540
00:34:59,240 --> 00:35:01,280
I will certainly get the truth

541
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,360
of Shanhai Gang.

542
00:35:31,960 --> 00:35:33,160
I’m really old.

543
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:37,160
I only delayed Qin Qi for four hours.

544
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:41,280
It’s not my time now!

545
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:42,880
Ten years ago,

546
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:45,920
they couldn’t leave Kaifeng.

547
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:47,920
Behave yourself!

548
00:35:48,040 --> 00:35:49,160
It’s you who hid from Lu Ping

549
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,320
and made him searching you.

550
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:51,320
Now that you

551
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:52,040
have made trouble,

552
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:53,720
you asked to solve the problem for him.

553
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:54,160
You…

554
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:58,600
What do you want?

555
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:02,000
That brat.

556
00:36:03,160 --> 00:36:04,280
He is upright.

557
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:08,960
I don’t want him to be misled.

558
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:17,120
Do you hurt again?

559
00:36:17,200 --> 00:36:18,440
Minmin, Minmin,Minmin.

560
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:19,440
Hurt! Hurt! Hurt!

561
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,560
It hurts!

562
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:25,760
Minmin,

563
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,720
can’t you be tender to me

564
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,960
since I am leaving?

565
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,130
Where are you going?

566
00:36:40,200 --> 00:36:41,840
Neither Qin Qi nor Shanhai Gang

567
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:44,400
would give up on Lu Ping.

568
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:50,280
I have to find a way to finish all these.

569
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,080
Old Guo.

570
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:12,320
Why? Hate to part with me?

571
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:19,520
I leave Ziyan to you.

572
00:37:21,160 --> 00:37:22,760
How good these children are!

573
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,800
They are like us in our younger days.

574
00:37:32,760 --> 00:37:34,400
We have wasted

575
00:37:37,600 --> 00:37:38,880
too much time.

576
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:19,560
Senior,

577
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:23,920
Lu Ping was injured badly

578
00:38:24,080 --> 00:38:25,560
but he didn’t hurt his vital parts.

579
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:27,160
Now he is safe.

580
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:28,600
That’s good.

581
00:38:30,640 --> 00:38:31,240
Senior,

582
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:34,200
we have kept the position

583
00:38:34,400 --> 00:38:36,440
of Master of Yaoguang Peak for you.

584
00:38:36,720 --> 00:38:38,680
Please return to your position.

585
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,920
The thing is there, but I’m no more the same one.

586
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:45,080
What’s the use of keeping it?

587
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:47,480
Senior!

588
00:38:54,120 --> 00:38:55,160
Senior.

589
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:57,940
Big Dipper is declining these years.

590
00:38:58,200 --> 00:38:59,800
I am an ordinary man.

591
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:01,600
But for the accident at that time,

592
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:03,530
and the leaving of all the masters,

593
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:07,120
I wouldn’t have become master of Big Dipper.

594
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:09,160
I’m inferior to Master Leng.

595
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:11,680
I have to take care

596
00:39:12,080 --> 00:39:14,040
and tolerate disapproval from others

597
00:39:14,040 --> 00:39:17,240
to keep the honor of Big Dipper.

598
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,520
Senior,

599
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:20,400
since you have come back,

600
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:23,880
you can’t leave it to me.

601
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:27,320
Li Yaotian.

602
00:39:30,200 --> 00:39:31,440
You are older than me.

603
00:39:31,640 --> 00:39:32,920
You have more gray hair than me.

604
00:39:32,920 --> 00:39:35,680
I think you are not lack of ability

605
00:39:37,120 --> 00:39:38,280
but courage.

606
00:39:38,880 --> 00:39:40,200
I can’t help you.

607
00:39:40,400 --> 00:39:42,320
Don’t bother me from then on.

608
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:44,290
Senior, one more question.

609
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:46,240
Hurry. I’m sleepy.

610
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:51,680
I heard from Miss Ling that

611
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:53,320
Lu Ping was the

612
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:56,080
disciple of Guo Youdao,

613
00:39:56,840 --> 00:40:00,000
and also the wanted man of the Shuo Country.

614
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,520
Is it right to take him

615
00:40:02,720 --> 00:40:03,580
up to Big Dipper

616
00:40:03,720 --> 00:40:05,040
in public?

617
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:06,040
And,

618
00:40:07,640 --> 00:40:09,280
who is Lu Ping?

619
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:11,140
What’s his relationship with

620
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,640
you and Senior Guo?

621
00:40:13,640 --> 00:40:17,200
You don’t have to know.

622
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:18,880
This child

623
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:21,520
must be safe.

624
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:23,520
Yes.

625
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,780
Senior, you must have forgotten.

626
00:40:29,080 --> 00:40:32,800
Master of Kaiyang Peak

627
00:40:33,200 --> 00:40:34,800
would care about everything

628
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:36,480
about Senior Guo.

629
00:40:38,200 --> 00:40:38,680
Shit!

630
00:40:39,480 --> 00:40:41,480
I forgot that old man!

631
00:40:42,560 --> 00:40:44,220
Why didn’t you say it earlier?

632
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:55,000
Master!

